title: I'm sorry Gezo
author: Celsius451
pages:
#- Gezo, I'm sorry that I killed you with lava yesterday. It was not at all my intention. My original plan, irrelevant now, was to trap you in the door thingy with lava on top of it for the lulz.
But that is not important now.

You lost some stuff
#- to the lava when you died. The diamond blocks are to compensate for it.

Once again, it was a total bonehead move. I luv u. pls forgive
#- pls
#- 